title: Fresh
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Russian, Delivey
description: Opened in Aug 2012 by the Canadian chain Fresh, this place is mostly vegan with some raw food and has a detox menu. Uses superfoods in dishes like acai, goji berry, guarana, spirulina, maca powder, wheatgrass, and hemp protein. Extensive menu includes veggie burgers, burritos, sandwich rolls, and a selection of snacks. Trendy and modern yet casual. Free Wi-Fi.
